      "comment": "SUMMER FAITH (6) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Wentworth Park behind Gillenbah Tiger (30.78) in a Mix 3/4. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Leading chance again. LUMEAH JOLIE (8) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when second (18.84) at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. LAGOON OHIYESA (1) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at Wagga over 320m behind Cawbourne Jemma (18.71) in a Grade 4/5. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from five starts. Should be thereabouts. PAW ULTRON (2) should be thereabouts.",
